data.title: High School Musical: The Series: Who is in the Disney+ cast?
data.meta_description: Get to know the cast of Disney+’s 'High School Musical: The Musical: The Series' here.
data.text:
Get to know the cast of Disney+’s 'High School Musical: The Musical: The Series' here.

1. Meet the cast of High School Musical: The Series on Disney+

'High School Musical: The Musical: The Series' is one of Disney+’s most popular shows. ‘HSMTMTS' is about the high school where 'High School Musical' was filmed putting on a production of 'High School Musical' and it is equal parts heartwarming and hilarious. Get to know the stars of the series here. [Disney+]

2. Who plays Nini in High School Musical: The Series? - Olivia Rodrigo

Olivia Rodrigo is the actress who plays Nini Salazar-Roberts in 'High School Musical: The Musical: The Series’ on Disney+. Nini is an aspiring musical theatre actress. She auditions to play Gabriella in the East High production of ‘High School Musical’. Olivia previously starred as Paige in 'Bizaardvark' on the Disney Channel. [Disney+]

3. Who plays Ricky in High School Musical: The Series? - Joshua Bassett

Joshua Basset is the actor who plays Ricky Bowen in 'High School Musical: The Musical: The Series’ on Disney+. Ricky previously dated Nini and he wants to play Troy in ‘High School Musical’ to win her back. Before ‘HSMTMTS’, Joshua guest-starred in ‘Grey’s Anatomy’ and ‘Dirty John’. [Disney+]

4. Who plays E.J. in High School Musical: The Series? - Matt Cornett

Matt Cornett plays the role of E.J. Caswell in 'High School Musical: The Musical: The Series' on Disney+. E.J. is a jock who fell for Nini at theatre camp after she broke up with Ricky. Matt is best known for playing Zach in ‘Bella and the Bulldogs’ on Nickelodeon. [Disney+]

5. Who plays Gina in High School Musical: The Series? - Sofia Wylie

Sofia Wylie is the actress behind Gina Porter in 'High School Musical: The Musical: The Series' on Disney+. Gina is a talented musical theatre enthusiast hellbent on playing Gabriella in ‘High School Musical’. You may recognise Sofia from her performance as Buffy in ‘Andi Mack’ on the Disney Channel. [Disney+]

6. Who plays Big Red in High School Musical: The Series? - Larry Saperstein

Larry Saperstein plays Big Red in 'High School Musical: The Musical: The Series' on Disney+. Big Red is Ricky’s best friend who does stage management for ‘High School Musical’ at East High. Larry is a professional tap dancer and he previously acted alongside Kiernan Shipka in the ABC film ‘Fan Girl’. [Disney+]

7. Who plays Ashlyn in High School Musical: The Series? - Julia Lester

Julia Lester acts the role of Ashlyn Caswell in 'High School Musical: The Musical: The Series' on Disney+. Ashlyn is E.J.’s cousin and an aspiring songwriter. Ashlyn has guest-starred in series including ‘Bella and the Bulldogs’ and ‘Mom’. [Disney+]

8. Who plays Kourtney in High School Musical: The Series? - Dara Reneé

Dara Renée stars as Kourtney in 'High School Musical: The Musical: The Series' on Disney+. Kourtney is Nini’s best friend who works in the East High theatre costume department in ‘HSMTMTS'. Dara is best-known for playing Stunts in ‘Black-ish’. [Disney+]

9. Who plays Carlos in High School Musical: The Series? - Frankie Rodriguez

Frankie Rodriguez plays Carlos Rodriguez in 'High School Musical: The Musical: The Series' on Disney+. Carlos is the choreographer of East High’s production of ‘High School Musical’ in ‘HSMTMTS’. Frankie has also starred as Mick in ‘I’m Fine’ and Eduardo in ‘Modern Family’. [Disney+]

10. Who plays Seb in High School Musical: The Series? - Joe Serafini

Joe Serafini is the actor who plays Sharpay in 'High School Musical: The Musical: The Series' on Disney+. Seb is cast as Sharpay in the school musical. ‘HSMTMTS’ is Joe’s first recurring role in a series. He has been upped to a main cast member for season 2. [Disney+]

11. Who plays Miss Jenn in High School Musical: The Series? - Kate Reinders

Kate Reinders stars as Miss Jenn in 'High School Musical: The Musical: The Series' on Disney+. Miss Jenn is East High’s drama teacher. She was also a background dancer in the first ‘High School Musical’ film. Kate is a prominent Broadway actress, most famous for playing Glinda in ‘Wicked’. [Disney+]

12. Who plays Mr. Mazzara in High School Musical: The Series? - Mark St. Cyr

Mark St. Cyr acts the role of Mr. Benjamin 'Ben' Mazzara in 'High School Musical: The Musical: The Series' on Disney+. Mr. Mazzara is East High’s STEM teacher and Miss Jenn’s nemesis. Mark has previously starred in ‘Giving Me Life (in the Land of the Deadass)’ and ‘The Verge’. [Disney+]
